{"tid":2113741,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"部分 Vpn 決定關閉香港伺服器 擔心國安法影響用家安全","createTime":"2020-07-18T10:17:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T02:17:08.000Z","uid":48083,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ee3e27d0a4a2337833a1b29042189502221dc177","tid":2113741,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T10:17:40.000Z","msg":"⋯據報導指，美國的 IPVanish 和 Private Internet Access，以及加拿大的 TunnelBear 都宣佈將會關閉香港伺服器，其中 IPVanish 在網誌中提到，目前他們已經關閉在香港的 VPN 伺服器並終止在香港的營運，他們解釋，國安法令原先作為網絡自由堡壘的香港，遭到與中國一樣嚴格的互聯網限制，而他們為了保障香港用家的自由，在目前視香港和中國成為一體的情況下，不得不作出這個決定。Private Internet Access 亦表示新法例對用戶和香港居民帶來風險，因此會抹消和關閉香港伺服器⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/07/18/vpn-firms-shut-down-hong-kong-servers-over-security-law-concerns/tech-secure/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F07%2F18%2Fvpn-firms-shut-down-hong-kong-servers-over-security-law-concerns%2Ftech-secure%2F&d=G%2B3HFD3c3HuaSfC8k9KTiVKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=78f4b78a\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/07/18/vpn-firms-shut-down-hong-kong-servers-over-security-law-concerns/tech-secure/</a>"},{"pid":"ad9dc16e9a8e1fca9830cd49d0a58bb4164a5290","tid":2113741,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T11:26:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5baa2330940b01e11991a2ed2f68947158caf71","tid":2113741,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T13:34:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200718/UINHXTAVMXD6EYMBYGBLXLQ3YI/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1FI8a2qQxnfcMcicfMyk0cexZWvfIFauEHjPNkb21_lJ4jagMaohAVEuk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200718%2FUINHXTAVMXD6EYMBYGBLXLQ3YI%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3